description:
Bright, budget hotel next to Gare du Nord and Gare de l'Est

Steps from 2 stations
This cost-effective hotel places you within 3 blocks of both Gare du Nord and Gare de l'Est train and metro stations. A metro ride takes you to top tourist spots like the Arc de Triomphe and the Louvre in under 25 minutes.

Holy history
You're less than 1 km from the pretty quays of the Canal St-Martin, lined with little bars and boutiques. Or you could head north and upwards into Montmartre's narrow streets Sacr-Coeur is a steepish 1.6 km away.

Bright and budget
Libertel Gare Du Nord Sude's colorful artwork and bright pink reception area give it a lively sense of character. Touches like free WiFi throughout add to this budget hotel's value. Clean-up your clothes with the hotel's dry cleaning services. Breakfast is on offer, too.

Rooms with a view
All guestrooms offer flat-screen TVs with satellite channels in addition to the basic amenities. Each room features artwork to liven things up, and some rooms have balconies. Guests like their clean functionality.

HOTEL_AMENITY.value: Libertel Gare Du Nord Suede features multilingual staff, coffee/tea in a common area, and complimentary newspapers in the lobby. Public areas are equipped with complimentary high-speed wireless Internet access. This Paris hotel also offers laundry facilities, dry cleaning/laundry services, and a safe deposit box at the front desk.

DINING.value: Buffet breakfasts are available for a surcharge and are served each morning between 6:30 AM and 10:30 AM.
